ces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f8592d1cd3fa75528fc0521be62fbfa906f163","tid":2517604,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0706615c54ad6483f5afad64572d541f9061fc8c","tid":2517604,"uid":6676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"有競爭有進步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"南韓：KBS MBC SBS TvN JTBC<br />\n香港：TVB TVB TVB TVB TVB"},{"pid":"e2f1bdc5c1ce4367d95abfd2443a662ad1e6808a","tid":2517604,"uid":217222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"我估:<br />\n當年嘉禾卡拉OK 已經播緊呢首歌:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wtXfp0mXpUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwtXfp0mXpUA&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=9fa0278c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wtXfp0mXpUA</a><br />\n<br />\n人地嘅影視圈都未必係差。<br />\n<br />\n未有互聯網前,<br />\n左抄右扮又好(例如綜藝), <br />\n買版權又好, 都係由娛樂公司選比當地民眾吸收。<br />\n不過自從互聯網打破地域限制之後, <br />\n就變左全世界一齊競爭。<br />\n變成韓國有機會跑出。<br />\n<br />\n同時, 日台港當年比較富裕同多生意來往,<br />\n所以做就娛樂圈相對成熟。<br />\n<br />\n然而2000左右, 大陸經濟起飛,<br />\n韓國地理位置近,<br />\n然後人種相近(大家都係北佬)<br />\n金日成死左, 危險程度低左,<br />\n加上韓國有大陸無嘅創意(相對高嘅民主同自由)<br />\n<br />\n食正晒大陸條水, <br />\n(日本又亡我之心不死)<br />\n所而有錢再加大發展, 成就今日韓國影視帝國。<br />\n<br />\n另外重有D, 韓仔鐘意賺你人仔, 話之你血唔血棉,童唔童工, <br />\n佢有錢賺, 學埋國語黎就你, <br />\n加更容易賺到大陸經濟起飛條水去發展影視。<br />\n<br />\n當然我唔覺得係邊個靠邊個,<br />\n生意嘅意各取所需。"},{"pid":"757fb2e82b29e64f569f17d6f8f5ed7e6b77dc84","tid":2517604,"uid":217222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f8592d1cd3fa75528fc0521be62fbfa906f163","tid":2517604,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0706615c54ad6483f5afad64572d541f9061fc8c","tid":2517604,"uid":6676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"有競爭有進步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"南韓：KBS MBC SBS TvN JTBC<br />\n香港：TVB TV